snippet.title: Kirby: Revenge of Dream Land - 1.0 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
It's finally here - the first release of Kirby: Revenge of Dream Land, with the completed Main Mode and The Arena available! Extra Mode and additional content will come in updates, so stay tuned~!

Download (Google Drive): https://drive.google.com/file/d/17yO_hz0zxBEmYn4R6MTFgSlfH9v09Dwa/view?usp=sharing
Download (Google Drive Mirror): https://drive.google.com/file/d/1V_RdvrXqzK2cR4yKvLY4FAEZQMw-n05X/view?usp=sharing 

Official RoDL Discord: https://discord.gg/skdD6PY
Follow me here: https://twitter.com/Luminous_Wish
